  "records": {
    "description": "Crafts colored boxes at 16gt, ideal for inputs of shulker loaders where you don't want to recolor boxes later. Based off of ACS006",
    "features": [
      "Crafts a colored box every 16gt",
      "Two versions: Regular Dye Input (Put crafted dye into the loader), Raw Dye Input (Put uncrafted dye into the loader (e.g., bonemeal))"
    ],
    "considerations": [
      "Breaks if it runs out of boxes",
      "Raw input must be 1 to 1, so no tall flowers",
      "Shulker unloaders cannot be activated within 4gt; there must be a difference in the log and shell and dye boxes. Follow the startup guide and always use full boxes to mitigate breakage"
    ],
    "instructions": [
      "After the build is complete, remove the two hoppers where the shell and log boxes will go and place those boxes facing down",
      "Take 8 logs out of the log box and craft them into 4 chests",
      "Place the chests in the middle crafter and replace the two hoppers",
      "Place the dye box and then put an item into the hopper with a comparator readout",
      "Take the item out and place it again, then take it out again"
    ],
    "notes": "Video of startup guide: https://youtu.be/llxf7ab16gw",
    "compatibility": "1.21+"
  },
